      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground">3. Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>This software is a third-party Minecraft launcher and is not affiliated with Mojang AB or Microsoft Corporation. Minecraft is a trademark of Mojang AB.</p>
