      <p>This software does not collect or upload any personal data. All configuration data is stored locally and is not sent to any remote server, except for services you explicitly use (e.g., Modrinth API, Minecraft authentication servers).</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground">6. Changes to This Agreement</h2>
      <p>We may update this agreement from time to time. Material changes will be announced via GitHub Releases. Continued use of the software constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground">7. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions, please reach out via <a href="https://github.com/Qomicex-Public/Qomicex.Tauri/issues" class="text-primary underline underline-offset-2" target="_blank">GitHub Issues</a>.</p>
